security_common_useragent



useragent检查


denylist
array[string]
黑名单列表，匹配User-Agent中的关键字，命中后拦截用户请求。

status
integer，默认值，403
拦截后，响应的状态码

message
string，
拦截后，响应的信息

bypass_missing
boolean，默认值，false
当设置为 true 时，如果User-Agent请求头不存在或格式有误时，将绕过检查。

说明：





事例：

添加插件
curl -L -X PUT 'http://127.0.0.1:9990/edge/admin/global_rules/6001' -H 'X-API-KEY: f9357106bff442f89d4de7169c37c61e' -H 'Content-Type: application/json' --data-raw '{
    "desc": "security_common",
    "plugins": {
        "security_common_useragent": {
            "bypass_missing": true,
            "denylist": [
                "jndi\\:(?:ldap|rmi|iiop|iiopname|corbaname|dns|nis)",
                "\\.(?:svn|htaccess|bash_history)",
                "\\.(?:bak|inc|old|mdb|sql|backup|java|class)$",
                "(?:vhost|bbs|host|wwwroot|www|site|root|hytop|flashfxp).*\\.rar",
                "(?:phpmyadmin|jmx-console|otsmobile/console|jmxinvokerservlet)",
                "\\'",
                "java\\.lang",
                "/(?:attachments|upimg|images|css|uploadfiles|html|uploads|templets|static|template|data|inc|forumdata|upload|includes|cache|avatar)/(\\w+)\\.(?:php|jsp)"
            ]
        }
    }
}'

测试
curl -L -X GET 'http://127.0.0.1:9980/hello1?test' -H 'User-Agent: PostmanRuntime/7.30.0 test.svn'

{"message":"Your request useragent is not allowed"}




